1
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:12,039
Zhou Yu.

2
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:22,120
Stop right there.

3
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:23,920
Stop.

4
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,289
Are you okay?

5
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:43,600
I'm fine.

6
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:45,580
Tell me.

7
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:47,240
What's your name?

8
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:48,600
What's your name?

9
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:54,680
Murder?

10
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,200
Officer,

11
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:59,370
I'm just a technician at an internet company.

12
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,400
How could I kill four people

13
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,600
in such a short time?

14
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:05,840
relatives, police officers, and relevant personnel.

15
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:03,520
Decided by the public security organ:

16
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,100
You say I'm a murderer.

17
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,400
Do you have any evidence?

18
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:16,640
Zhou Yu.

19
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:19,620
This gateway was found in your house.

20
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:22,700
You used it to send text messages to the four of them.

21
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,840
Your fingerprints are on it.

22
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:27,460
What else do you have to say for yourself?

23
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,560
Officer.

24
00:02:30,079 --> 00:02:31,240
You might not know,

25
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:33,640
I don't just do network maintenance.

26
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:34,600
I also have a part-time job

27
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:36,530
flipping used computer hardware.

28
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:37,360
Well,

29
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:40,320
if someone tampered with this hardware

30
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:41,960
or broke any laws with it,

31
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:43,000
how would I know?

32
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:44,400
Besides,

33
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,160
I just resell them.

34
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:48,930
It's normal to have my fingerprints on it,

35
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:50,000
right?

36
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:54,890
You can leave first.

37
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:07,640
Zhou Yu,

38
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:09,400
male, 30 years old.

39
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,320
Lost his father at a young age

40
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:11,780
and lived with his mother.

41
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,640
Graduated high school with excellent grades

42
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:16,200
and got into the law department of Jiangcheng University.

43
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,400
According to the investigation,

44
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,640
during your time at school, because of your outstanding grades

45
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:20,520
and introverted personality,

46
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,800
you were envied and bullied by Xu Xing, Lin Ran,

47
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:24,120
Li Xiaoru, and Zhao Wenbing.

48
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:26,800
During that time, to resolve the issue, your mother

49
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:29,360
was humiliated by the four of them in front of your classmates,

50
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,840
and beaten to the point of disability.

51
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:33,040
But for various reasons, it ended in a private settlement.

52
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:35,440
In your junior year, you were disfigured by an acid attack.

53
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,770
So you chose to drop out.

54
00:03:40,160 --> 00:03:41,040
After dropping out,

55
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:42,560
you taught yourself hacking skills

56
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,840
and worked in internet cafe tech maintenance.

57
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:45,720
During this time,

58
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:49,400
you hacked into Xu Xing, Lin Ran, Li Xiaoru, and Zhao Wenbing's accounts multiple times.

59
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,800
And Wang Min's computer.

60
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,000
But,

61
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:12,760
this is no excuse for you to defy the law and commit crimes.

62
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:21,399
He has confessed

63
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,840
that you used the internet

64
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:25,170
to instruct him to send the death notices.

65
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:26,480
And here is

66
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:29,240
the evidence our cybersecurity officers

67
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:32,770
found of your long-term surveillance of Xu Xing and the others.

68
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:35,920
That's right.

69
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:39,460
All I did was create a murder mystery game

70
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:41,240
and send a few text messages.

71
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,640
And what was the result?

72
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:44,640
They started turning on each other.

73
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:50,159
And the elevator at Zhao Wenbing's house,

74
00:04:50,159 --> 00:04:51,760
you controlled it remotely,

75
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:54,440
which almost caused him to suffocate to death.

76
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:55,200
So what?

77
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:57,320
He deserved to die.

78
00:04:57,960 --> 00:05:00,520
This is just the bitter fruit they sowed.

79
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:02,760
When you were bullied back then,

80
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:04,360
you should have called the police.

81
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,420
Why wait until now?

82
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:09,450
Call the police?

83
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,320
Officer,

84
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:14,130
is it useful to call the police?

85
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:16,640
The school also investigated and punished them.

86
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:17,920
But what happened afterwards?

87
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,440
I was still excluded,

88
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:22,000
humiliated, and bullied.

89
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:25,880
The thing I regret most in my life

90
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:29,000
is listening to my mother.

91
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,400
She thought

92
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,480
studying

93
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:36,480
could change my destiny.

94
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:38,560
I tried.

95
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:40,800
I obeyed.

96
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,200
I did as she said.

97
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:47,200
I studied hard and got into a university with great teachers.

98
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,940
But after I went there, I found out

99
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:56,120
I was like a sheep entering a pack of wolves.

100
00:05:57,400 --> 00:06:00,080
This shouldn't be your excuse for committing crimes.

101
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:00,680
No.

102
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:03,760
They deserved to die.

103
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:06,240
My mother went to the school

104
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:08,080
to stand up for me,

105
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:10,640
and they pushed her off the building alive.

106
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:15,080
Hey,

107
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,690
why are you stopping me?

108
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:17,840
Ma'am,

109
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:18,800
your son

110
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:20,480
stole her first place in the competition.

111
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:20,920
Huh?

112
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,840
Your son is quite capable.

113
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:25,000
How is that possible?

114
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,080
I had no idea.

115
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,530
She didn't know.

116
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:28,820
Stop the nonsense.

117
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:30,480
Ma'am,

118
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:32,680
don't you want to go back

119
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:34,280
and ask your son properly?

120
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,240
Mom!

121
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,040
Mom!

122
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:50,560
Mom!

123
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,480
Mom, what's wrong?

124
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:53,960
It hurts.

125
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:55,480
It hurts.

126
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:57,400
My whole body hurts.

127
00:06:59,240 --> 00:06:59,920
You...

128
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:03,720
Mom,

129
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,560
are you okay?

130
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:08,020
I'll take you to the hospital right now, Mom.

131
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,680
Multiple fractures all over the body.

132
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:10,640
And then?

133
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,920
The school made them apologize.

134
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:14,520
Xu Xing just gave 100,000.

135
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,740
With just 100,000,

136
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:18,080
he made my mom shut up.

137
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:20,260
But what happened?

138
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:24,280
My mom died less than a year later.

139
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:26,840
But look at them.

140
00:07:26,840 --> 00:07:28,040
Look at them.

141
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:30,620
They thought my family was easy to bully,

142
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,880
and abused me even worse,

143
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:35,080
hurting me.

144
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:38,520
Right in front of me,

145
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:39,580
they abused my cat,

146
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,760
and pushed my head into the sink.

147
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,560
They splashed acid on my face,

148
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,880
disfiguring me.

149
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:46,080
They ruined my life,

150
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:47,280
and killed my mom.

151
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,600
They deserve to die.

152
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,480
Calm down.

153
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:56,060
You were already an adult.

154
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:59,130
You could have used legal means

155
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,400
to solve the problem,

156
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:01,920
instead of choosing the wrong path

157
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:04,050
and dragging yourself into the abyss.

158
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:08,760
Officer Qiu,

159
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,220
do you think

160
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:14,360
my revenge was a success?

161
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:20,440
In that gateway and memory card,

162
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,660
there is something I left for you.

163
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:26,040
We

164
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:29,400
will never stop taking revenge.

165
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:48,360
Qiu Chen,

166
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:49,720
congratulations.

167
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:51,920
You have successfully passed my three tests.

168
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:53,720
I will tell you my next target.

169
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:56,200
But the file will self-destruct in one second.

170
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,080
Good luck.

171
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,480
Go back.

172
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,360
Don't stop me.

173
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:08,440
It's a trap.

174
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:10,000
What if he really is the Scavenger?

175
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:12,260
Police don't make deals with criminals.

176
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:14,960
What's going on?

177
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,020
What are you doing?

178
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:16,960
Oh.

179
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:18,120
We are

180
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:19,320
discussing the case.

181
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:21,200
Yes.

182
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:23,320
Do you think I'm deaf?

183
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:25,760
Don't think I don't know what you are trying to do.

184
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:27,880
Failing to report a case truthfully

185
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,610
has serious consequences.

186
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:30,890
Chief Zhang,

187
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:31,520
I apply

188
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,600
to reopen the investigation of the Scavenger case.

189
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,130
Qiu Chen,

190
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,260
attention!

191
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,360
For future cases,

192
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:41,290
if there are any clues related to the Scavenger case,

193
00:09:41,560 --> 00:09:43,080
you must report them immediately.

194
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,840
The higher-ups will review and decide

195
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:46,680
whether you need to recuse yourself.

196
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:47,880
If you don't report it

197
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:49,640
and investigate without authorization,

198
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:51,640
you will face disciplinary action.

199
00:09:51,800 --> 00:09:52,530
Chief Zhang,

200
00:09:53,040 --> 00:09:53,640
he just...

201
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,800
Follow the order.

202
00:09:55,400 --> 00:09:55,930
Yes, sir.

203
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:56,900
Get out.

204
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,320
Gu Yuming.

205
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:01,920
Here.

206
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:04,000
Go back to your captain's office.

207
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,060
Stay away from him.

208
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,200
So you two don't cause trouble for me every day.

209
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:07,460
Yes.

210
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:08,360
And,

211
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:11,240
regarding the reopening of the Scavenger case,

212
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:12,680
you must keep it strictly confidential

213
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:13,640
from Qiu Chen.

214
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:15,400
He is too young.

215
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:16,480
I'm worried he

216
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:17,850
might act impulsively.

217
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:19,650
Understood.

218
00:10:19,680 --> 00:10:20,280
Remember that.

219
00:10:20,280 --> 00:10:20,680
Got it.

220
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:22,240
Get back to work.

221
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:22,640
Yes.

222
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:52,650
Ouch.

223
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,120
Need any help?

224
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:57,490
Director Zhang said

225
00:10:57,760 --> 00:10:59,360
to keep my distance from you.

226
00:11:00,640 --> 00:11:02,900
When have you ever listened to warnings?

227
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,040
Cut the crap

228
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,320
and help out.

229
00:11:18,560 --> 00:11:20,360
Why are you just standing there?

230
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:23,320
Hey.

231
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:24,720
What about my flowers?

232
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:25,560
Oh.

233
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:30,680
And this.

234
00:11:33,920 --> 00:11:34,400
Got it.

235
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,280
Let's go.

236
00:11:58,800 --> 00:11:59,720
So clumsy.

237
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:01,450
What kind of broken box is this?

238
00:12:01,560 --> 00:12:02,760
Hurry up and clean it.

239
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:46,920
The Scavenger has struck twice in a row.

240
00:12:46,920 --> 00:12:47,980
Clues are missing.

241
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:56,330
Evidence is still missing.

242
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:58,080
The Scavenger's motive

243
00:12:58,400 --> 00:12:59,000
is unknown.
